# Skills: single source of truth

- **All Agent Skills for this project live in `.cursor/skills/`.**
- When adding or editing skills, change **only** `.cursor/skills/<skill-name>/`.

## Exception: converter playbooks

**Converter-specific logic** belongs in:

- `converters/<id>/playbook/SKILL.md` — apply/sync
- `converters/<id>/playbook/VERIFICATION.md` — capture, compare, remediate
- `converters/<id>/playbook/VERIFIER.md` — verify agent

**Conversion output** (sync status, projects) lives in `conversions/<id>/`.

Do not describe `conversions/<id>/` as "conversion status" when answering **converter readiness** — only as verify-harness location for converter dev tasks. See [converter-vs-conversion.mdc](../rules/converter-vs-conversion.mdc).

These are loaded by path when **sync-target**, **conversion-loop**, or verifier agents route to a converter. Do not duplicate converter playbooks into `.cursor/skills/`.

See [CONVERTER_VS_CONVERSION.md](../skills/harmony-conversion/reference/CONVERTER_VS_CONVERSION.md).
